item.title: CVE-2022-1846|2024-08-03T00:17:00.834Z -- unknown -- tiny%20contact%20form
item.description: The Tiny Contact Form WordPress plugin through 0.7 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack
